def days_of_weeks(N: int, K: int) -> list[int]:
    days_count = [N // 7] / 7
    remaining_days = N % 7
    for i in range(remaining_days):
        day_index = (K - 1 + i) % 7
        days_count[day_index] += 1
    return days_count
